events.text: Every night feels never ending and I swear everyone in this town wants to talk my ear off
All I have to entertain myself is my phone and the voice inside my head
I can't believe Becky made me take over working nights for her...but she makes the schedule so what the hell can I do about it...
Plus...there are no other jobs in this shithole town...so whatever.
My dad's the only reason I have this job...but he picked Becky over me to run the place.
I'm so tired, I can barely remember my name...what is it again?
